  "bio": "Brett F. Miller is the incumbent Place 2 trustee on the Longview ISD Board of Trustees. A Longview native and third-generation Longview High School graduate, he practices family law, employment disputes, and business litigation at Miller Fair Henry PLLC. First elected in 2020 after challenging incumbent Ava Welge, he was unopposed for reelection in 2023. He holds a J.D. from SMU Dedman School of Law and an undergraduate degree from Texas Christian University.",
